title: Trump Hoped for a Celebration but Did Not Have Much to Cheer
description: The former president endorsed roughly 300 candidates in the midterm elections. With votes still being counted, those in competitive races appeared to have mixed results.
dc:creator: Michael C. Bender and Maggie Haberman
media:credit: Josh Ritchie for The New York Times
media:description: Former President Donald J. Trump speaking Tuesday at an election night party at his Mar-a-Lago resort in Palm Beach, Fla.
